reviewText: My Father in law likes this stuff, so I guess they are good

e-mailed vendor who did nothing but ignore....  the movie itself was extremely good.... but the cheap quality of the dvd was not.... asked for replacement but there was no response at all, dvd was expensive at $20... they could have at least sent a replacement.... I could have returned the box....
Coco Martin exudes lots of charisma.  I also see a very talented actor for a long time in Philippine cinema.  Awesome feel good comedy drama.
